item.description:
Manchester business owners and entrepreneurs at all levels are invited to join Debby Hoffman Adair and Linda Kaye from 9-11am on Tuesday, August 14 for a CEO Coffee Chat.

Our host for this meeting is Wall Street Towers Luxury Apartments. Â We'll be meeting in their beautiful function room overlooking the Merrimack River.

The meeting is FREE, the coffee (or tea) is on us, and the chat will be geared for your success.
item.how_to_find_us: Park in Guest Parking - Tell them in the Lobby you are here for the CEO Coffee Chat
